data.description: LOOK NO FURTHER! YOUR SPORTSMANS SANCTUARY IS HERE! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 60 x 27 double wide has plenty of star features! Laminate Flooring throughout, spacious master chefs kitchen with island for extra cooking room and entertaining, wood burning fireplace, and indoor laundry room. Enjoy the sunny Florida days in the screen enclosed porch and have your fun in the sun by taking a dip in the 12 x 24 above ground vinyl pool with an automatic cleaner! Bring your Boat, RV, Trucks, Trailers, and more because within all the space of your fully fenced 1 acre property, is a 2 car carport with attached storage shed, 1 car detached garage with power, wood deck under awning for private entry, AND 5 additional sheds giving additional space for all your toys! Few leasing restrictions for this to be an income producing property. 5 different Boat Ramps WITHIN 3.5 MILES, Biking and Walking Trails, Equestrian Hikes, and right by the Withlacoochee River leading into the Bay for your fisherman paradise to be complete! CALL TODAY BEFORE THIS ONE GETS AWAY!
